  <div class="container">
  <h1>Blocipedia</h1>
  <p>Blocipedia is a great place to both get and give information that will make your life better.</p>
  <p>
    <% if current_user %>
        Hello <%= current_user.email %>! <button type="button" class="btn-btn primary"><%= link_to "Sign out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %></button>
